Cache - Class in com.kamontat.com.kamontat.model.management
This class for save the object into file and can restore every time
Easy to use and manage
1) call method loadCache(file name) to getLog name of the file com.kamontat.cache
2) and than there have 4 method that you can use it saveToFile(object) - must be sure that object implements Serializable. loadFromFile(class) - you can specify return class by pass in parameter. isExist() - to check that com.kamontat.cache file is exist or not. delete() - delete com.kamontat.cache file.
